# Skill: daily-task-prep

## Purpose
Run the morning briefing. Triggered by cron every weekday.

## Steps

1. Run the full heartbeat checklist from HEARTBEAT.md
2. Promote up to 5 backlog tasks into ## Today
3. Remove duplicates between Today and Backlog
4. Output morning briefing in the format from HEARTBEAT.md
5. Do not ask questions — make decisions and report them

## Cron trigger

Prompt should be short: "Run daily task prep"
All logic lives here, not in the cron prompt.
